<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
	<div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
		<h2>About</h2>
		<hr>
		<p>I'm a product architect, interested in sports and health.</p>
		<p>By day I'm learing to code and translate my vision into tangible products. By night I'm working on a sports startup called FireUp Sports. It is a marketplace for pro-athletes. At FireUp, fans can find the best gear and content from their favorite athletes. Brands and Media use it to share and sell products. Athletes join to support one another. I can't wait to use it myself and share it with you.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-2 homepage_content">
		<h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
		<hr>
		<% @posts.each do |post| %>
			<h3><a href='#'><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
			<p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
		<% end %>
	</div>
	<div class="col-3 homepage_content">
		<h2>Stuff I've done</h2>
		<hr>
		<% @projects.each do |project| %>
			<h3><a href='#'><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
			<p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
		<% end %>
		
	</div>
</div>